The paper deals with the storage and retrieval of data using DNA molecules, which involves issues related to data security, data structures, databases, information theory, and software engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.DB (Databases), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
